## RBAC probing (important)

Deliberately attempt at least a few actions this persona should NOT be allowed to do
(navigate to a higher-privilege route by URL, attempt a restricted mutation). Record the
outcome precisely:

- **Blocked correctly** → note it (this is a passing control worth reporting as VERIFIED-OK).
- **Allowed when it should not be** → this is a **Critical RBAC finding**. Capture the request
  method/path/status that performed the action, and whether it persisted on reload.

